"If we carefully analyze the speech of the President of the United States, the speech of the foreign Minister of Germany, I do not take Ukraine, Georgia, or British, in any case, the choir was not absolutely accurate,"-drew the attention of the politician, Noticing that Russia "was no longer a wall, which is being coached by tennis ball."
