RUSSIAN Ministry of Finance predicts ruble exchange rate for 17 years ahead
The Russian Ministry of Finance expects a gradual weakening of the ruble-up to 73.9 rubles. For the dollar by 2031-2035 years, follows from the project of long-term budget forecast, made in the State Duma together with the draft federal budget.
In 2021-2025, the ruble rate, according to the forecast, will be 66.4 rubles per dollar, in 2026-2030 years-71.1 rubles, and in the next five years-73.9.
