Real effective course (the indicator, taking into account the change of exchange rates of the countries which are the main trading partners of the Russian Federation) will remain stable, officials assure.
As for inflation, up to 2020 it will be 3.5%, and then stabilize at about 4%, the Ministry of Finance believes.
